{"tid":2230324,"cid":4,"subCid":0,"title":"Apple申請氫燃料電池專利   MacBook、iPad或可數週不用充電","createTime":"2020-10-05T00:26:57.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-24T05:21:32.000Z","uid":22675,"like":26,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"08a7605d03590141c1787061b15368ad63a91202","tid":2230324,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T00:26:57.000Z","msg":"根據《Techrader》報道，Apple 正研究一種能輕易攜帶、經濟，高效能的全新燃料電池，也就是將氫轉化為電能的「質子交換膜（PEM）燃料電池」。<br />\n <br />\nApple 已在 2010 年開始有使用氫燃料電池的想法，在 2015 年再次提出。不過他們亦提到，要設計一款可在流動裝置上使用，而且合符成本效益的氫電池並不容易。<br />\n <br />\n報道指 Apple 除了氫燃料之外，也有固體氧化物燃料電池、熔融碳酸鹽燃料電池、直接甲醇燃料電池，鹼性燃料電池等方案。"},{"pid":"f536288b69c48afc7edee002f109d6ec90670c1f","tid":2230324,"uid":156096,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T00:27:25.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e0c8839add24320ea8ccd7bdeac8e49bd168888f","tid":2230324,"uid":120955,"like":11,"dislike":40,"score":-29,"citedBy":9,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T00:43:07.000Z","msg":"未有技術量產到就霸鳩個專利先"},{"pid":"5f7cf728c9727462be4c181fc1d42ed5c656a24d","tid":2230324,"uid":370061,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T01:05:16.000Z","msg":"氫電池？！會唔會boooooooooom！<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa494c7d644bd5ffce45818871910f5716f3fbb1","tid":2230324,"uid":90749,"like":31,"dislike":0,"score":31,"quote":{"pid":"e0c8839add24320ea8ccd7bdeac8e49bd168888f","tid":2230324,"uid":120955,"like":11,"dislike":40,"score":-29,"citedBy":9,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T00:43:07.000Z","msg":"未有技術量產到就霸鳩個專利先"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T01:12:04.000Z","msg":"R&amp;D 不嬲都係咁玩"},{"pid":"787a4a5adb3dee2550a1c98edd18798a5f099d3a","tid":2230324,"uid":197393,"like":41,"dislike":0,"score":41,"quote":{"pid":"e0c8839add24320ea8ccd7bdeac8e49bd168888f","tid":2230324,"uid":120955,"like":11,"dislike":40,"score":-29,"citedBy":9,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T00:43:07.000Z","msg":"未有技術量產到就霸鳩個專利先"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-05T06:05:46.000Z","msg":"不嬲都係發明就